p: The extracts of different parts (roots, seeds, leaves, and capitula) were analysed by GC/MS. As shown in Table 5 and Figure 1, GC/MS analysis confirmed the presence of twenty compounds in extracts studied, including N-isobutyl-dodeca-2,4,8,10-tetraenamide, N-isobutyl-2,4-octadiene-6-monoynamide, levulinic acid, propanedioic acid, palmitic acid, morphinan-6-One,4,5.Alpha.-epoxy-3-hydroxy-17-methyl, 2,4-undecadiene-8,10-diyne- N-tyramide, and dodeca-2 E,4 E,n E-trienoic acid 4-hydroxyphenylethylamide.
